If you go with Pre-Cached there are following things
1. Its lightening fast, as we don't need to touch the actual tree again
2. Its fail safe iterator, means andy modification in actual tree won't affect this [ use in concurent system]
3. It consume lot of memory as we need to cache whole tree (O(n))
4. next() and hashNext() is constant time. 


