I am writing this solution to people who are struggling with TME and beginners who are finding difficult to understand other solution in a easy manner.

**Intution:**
Once I saw the solution I thought this the approach should be to go for priority queue and write away wrote an approach finding all the sum combination by nums1 * nums2 and storing in priority queue.

Something like this..
```
    public List<List<Integer>> kSmallestPairs1(int[] nums1, int[] nums2, int k) {
